<p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718168794312008615.png" title="1718168794312008615.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-06-12 125449.png" width="833" height="702" style="width: 833px; height: 702px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">在信息的海洋中,<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-align: center;">我们携手前行</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">融媒体协会，如灯塔般明亮。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">智慧与创新，是我们的旗帜，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">连接你我他，传递新闻的力量。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">我们是经济管理学院融媒体协会!!!</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1.“融”会贯通，锦上添花</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718168308815087650.png" title="1718168308815087650.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-06-12 125131.png" width="943" height="517" style="width: 943px; height: 517px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">文字与图像，交织成美妙的乐章，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">在网络的舞台上，我们共同演绎。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">分享与互动，让我们的心灵相通，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">打破时空的界限，让知识无界飞翔。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">2.往期精彩推文集锦</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718168565822093496.png" style="" title="1718168565822093496.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718168567266008251.png" style="" title="1718168567266008251.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718168568482090697.png" style="" title="1718168568482090697.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718168568894075911.png" style="" title="1718168568894075911.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718168570194015175.png" style="" title="1718168570194015175.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718168570601053805.png" style="" title="1718168570601053805.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">我们用文字编织梦想，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">记录瞬间，描绘未来。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">每一个字句，都饱含深情，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">让知识的火花，在其间绽放。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">在融媒体的舞台上，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">我们汇聚智慧，碰撞思想。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">每一次交流，都是一次成长，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">让创新成为我们前进的动力。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">3.逐影校园，创意不止</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718168732070087473.png" style="" title="1718168732070087473.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718168733889029658.png" style="" title="1718168733889029658.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718169004896051959.png" title="1718169004896051959.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-06-12 131007.png" width="902" height="612" style="width: 902px; height: 612px;"/></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">（信息部成员活跃于每一个活动现场)</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718169087399009949.png" style="" title="1718169087399009949.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718169089840017510.png" style="" title="1718169089840017510.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718169163611034485.png" style="" title="1718169163611034485.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718169164430044314.png" style="" title="1718169164430044314.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">(各部门招新面试过程中)</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">我们用心倾听，每一个声音，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">让故事在笔尖流淌，让情感在屏幕绽放。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">我们勇敢创新，探索未知的领域，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">让科技与艺术，在融媒体的舞台交融。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">4.青春“视”界，聚焦美好</span><br/></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718169233063056496.png" style="" title="1718169233063056496.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; 